@yslbeauty took a page out of K-beauty classics with their new cushion foundation, and our Social Creative Lead, @tashasheridan, put it to the test for our next #TryHard. The buildable formula makes it easy to play with, whether you’re going for full glam or a natural, everyday finish.
We recently spoke with @charli_xcx, who told us, “It just gives a very soft, glowy look, and it’s not something that you need to reapply. You can just put it on, it wears all day, but it doesn’t feel heavy, which is my dream in any makeup product, but particularly in a foundation.”
And while the foundation itself delivers, the compact is something to write home about in its own right. The formula practically melts into the skin, making it the perfect lightweight base and your new go-to foundation for summer.

